  "signal_description": "The query retrieves data from the table 'defaultview-545'. It calculates the average cycle time from the creation of a purchase order (PO) item to the receipt of an invoice. The cycle time is calculated by subtracting the timestamp of the first 'Create PO Item' event from the timestamp of the last 'Receive invoice' event. The result is grouped by quarter and also includes the 'PO Item Line Type' column."
